reviews:
Update - it works now..lol.. We found that the A and B buttons (A) turns on different colour lights and also (B) used to dim the intensity.

Disregard this: Worked great for a LITTLE while, now it turns on but no light from the four built in LED's??? So needless to say, no skylights. Poor quality, buy elsewhere.

review_title: Excellent quality tempered glass screen protector
reviews: Just like the title states, also goes on easy, comes with 3 prep/cleaning kits and what seems like a plastic placement that fits the edge of the phone all around. I guess this helps center the screen protector while installing. I've done so many, I never used it but comes in very handy if you're new at this. Very fast shipping!

Great drone, seems to be a solid build! Had an issue with one of the sensors and the seller promptly shipped a replacement out! This is why I prefer to buy made(or at least serviced) in USA/Canada! Overall a great experience with the product and seller! Would definitely buy from again.

I was reading on how to cool down my ASUS AC2400 router, not sure why ASUS wouldn't add some heat escape holes at the top as they did the side and bottom. Removed top of router, made a large hole and drilled smaller holes to secure the fan to the top by removing the 4 bottom silicone mats/feet. Works like a champ, on low, the router is now cold to the touch as compared to before when it was a like a hot-plate. With the bearings rated at 67000 hours, should be good for 7-8 years of service (hopefully). Love the fan and the router!
Nice and large and slow rising, great deal overall. Fast shipping!
Good speaker, exactly like the original is replaced!

Wasn't sure what to expect, but when I opened the package I was amazed with the quality! Durable shell material, lot's of pockets, quality zippers and shoulder strap with padding. It fit my 13" laptop, mouse, power cord, I also keep a small 5 port POE network switch with a couple of cables handy, for work and that fit in the rear pocket (I got the large black). Basically, much more compact than what I was using, all in a compact unit slung out back, keeping my hands free to hold my coffee..lol
My only gripe is, there isn't any padding at the bottom to protect laptops, but an easy fix as I just cut a piece of foam I had laying around and voila, padded bottom! Or any sponge from a dollar store would work, just cut it to size.
Perfect as expected since I've already ordered seven!! And FAST...shipping!!

review_title: Runs perfect every year and family loves it!!
reviews: We have had this for 9 years now, runs perfect every year, just make sure and clean the tracks at the start of the season, I use WD40 with a cloth, keeps it running without any stops.Never had it come off the tracks yet, not sure how some are saying it does? Maybe tracks arent; locked together properly? Kids love it and look forward to it every year, especially the big ones..lol, I can sit and watch it for hours, fireplace on and some nice music playing! Hope you enjoy it like we do.
